original_title: 獣拳戦隊ゲキレンジャーギュンギュン！拳聖大運動会
overview: After their latest win, the three Gekirangers find the Kensei stretching for their annual Kensei Great Athletic Meet. Jan, wanting to win the gold medal and a year's supply of Televi magazines, joins the Red Team to go against the White Team. With Retsu as judge and Ran as moderator, the contest starts...
title: Juken Sentai Gekiranger: Gyun-Gyun! Fist Sage Great Athletic Meet
